  Locus:
    Page: 163
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Fault
---
When any fit of gloominess or perversion of mind lays hold of you, make it
a rule not to publish it by complaints, but exert your whole care to hide
it. By endeavoring to hide it, you will drive it away.
